{"tid":2370603,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"伊朗導彈射近美艦  落特朗普面 尼米茲號留守","createTime":"2021-01-18T07:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T07:40:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5812ba03df9432bd7a3629742eec103c520f0ddc","tid":2370603,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:08:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210118/SJKXZWEGTFBLPC6SX4H25KV5QA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210118%2FSJKXZWEGTFBLPC6SX4H25KV5QA%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=faf2819a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210118%2FSJKXZWEGTFBLPC6SX4H25KV5QA%2F&h=73a91eb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210118/SJKXZWEGTFBLPC6SX4H25KV5QA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n伊朗導彈射近美艦 <br />\n落特朗普面 尼米茲號留守<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xWXdXsNVUGbXxpewdZgWWlBViLQ=/2953x1968/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JOLT26JASZCDFGSSUGOCOTYIZ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxWXdXsNVUGbXxpewdZgWWlBViLQ%3D%2F2953x1968%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJOLT26JASZCDFGSSUGOCOTYIZ4.jpg&h=86bd20d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■伊朗軍事動作頻繁，上周五在中部的軍事演習同時發射多枚導彈。 法新社<br />\n<br />\n中東局勢持續緊張，伊朗前日朝阿拉伯海目標發射多枚反艦彈道導彈，儼如向其對頭、即將下台的美國總統特朗普示威贈興。霍士新聞獨家報道，有導彈落在區內游弋的美軍「尼米茲號」航空母艦打擊群和一艘商船附近。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：德黑蘭產鈾 英法德轟核威脅<br />\n<br />\n伊朗伊斯蘭革命衞隊聲稱這次被稱為「偉大先知15」的導彈試射，成功擊中1,800公里外的靶艦，革命衞隊司令薩拉米直言，「我們其中一個防衞政策及戰略，便是要以彈道導彈打中敵人的軍艦，包括航母及巡洋艦」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美軍不視為威脅<br />\n<br />\n霍士引述消息指，至少兩枚伊朗導彈擊中海面時爆炸，碎片四飛，有導彈落點在尼米茲航母打擊群的160公里外，但既不在視線範圍內，飛行軌迹也全程受到美國間諜衞星監控，美軍判斷伊軍試射只屬例行訓練，因此並無發出警報。報道引述一名官員表示：「我們早已預期會有導彈發射」。尼米茲航母打擊群原本本月初折返美國，但途中突然接到五角大樓命令，要艦隊繼續駐守區內，直至候任總統拜登上場。<br />\n<br />\n外界關注的是，當時其中一枚伊朗長程導彈落在商船外32公里的水域，有危。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n前天的反艦彈道導彈試射也是伊朗為報復美軍暗殺其將領蘇萊曼尼，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n晒新款自殺式無人機<br />\n<br />\n雖然對伊朗較為友善的拜登即將上台，有望緩和特朗普任內緊張的美伊關係，但近期德黑蘭仍頻頻有軍事動作，除試射彈道導彈和巡航導彈，又展示新款自殺式無人機及一艘由運油輪改裝成的直升機母艦。<br />\n<br />\n美軍也採取相應行動，除了尼米茲航母打擊群外，早前也派出B-52戰略轟炸機飛臨波斯灣上空，連番進行威懾性巡邏，上周更罕有讓載有150多枚戰斧巡航導彈的「喬治亞號」核攻擊潛艇，在霍爾木茲海峽附近的伊軍演習範圍若隱若現示威。 <br />\n<br />\n半島電視台<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RbmLJlMZJ2-7DkjlsPBPLDBoQ1s=/1774x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PJP3DMSY5NH7ZI6IFL7I2WR7GU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRbmLJlMZJ2-7DkjlsPBPLDBoQ1s%3D%2F1774x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPJP3DMSY5NH7ZI6IFL7I2WR7GU.jpg&h=283136f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■導彈落於美軍「尼米茲號」航母160公里外。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NSfUlKbnQqWoXJGrIocHDHp9398=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XIP34F3XPJEKJN5RPDSJ25SANQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNSfUlKbnQqWoXJGrIocHDHp9398%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXIP34F3XPJEKJN5RPDSJ25SANQ.jpg&h=3973313e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■伊朗反美情緒持續高漲。 資料圖片"},{"pid":"fb1dee35eab2d60837756f34c90cc072ea725c0f","tid":2370603,"uid":199669,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:10:12.000Z","msg":"波斯灣gg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歐洲，自己的事自己做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1178afdbb2e801e3e3325a48b2a594ae3a074713","tid":2370603,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:12:08.000Z","msg":"160公里外<img src=\"/ass